{"tid":1743222,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府換票箱既可行性有幾大？","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T16:25:42.000Z","uid":131259,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6de63df5138f47e80f0c295131c4d611ad7f5e5d","tid":1743222,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Fp_cs.html&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=2cd7fdfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html</a><br />\n先唔講保皇黨種票同民意<br />\n根據政府個網 大部分票站都會即場點票<br />\n但投完票之後要清場改裝先再開放比人入<br />\n中間個段時間係無公眾監察到<br />\n經過依半年個個都知依個政府有幾狗<br />\n有cctv 監察人員乜鳩都係假<br />\n無公眾監察到就無保障<br />\n但依家咁有個空窗期<br />\n佢成個票箱換左去都得<br />\n有咩可以保障番選舉公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 點都好 都要去投左先"},{"pid":"99f7f5e91d907f46f17aee02b35d33d2c5590690","tid":1743222,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad0dc33598e7f591826d9508aead29f38d864af7","tid":1743222,"uid":33293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa58d65133e03c4b4cff9ac9140d40af8df39ff1","tid":1743222,"uid":72381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"100%<br />\n老鼠曾咪咁淡定囉"},{"pid":"31e4850eb8cafca0b5bf7f2107a6800d086c5449","tid":1743222,"uid":121255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"每個候選人都有一個監察人<br />\n到時可以留係票站觀察整個過程 靠哂佢"},{"pid":"5719df3f8cec38418cb1b2f68f17c7f4788569f7","tid":1743222,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"候選人可以派人一直睇住<br />\n所以呢樣靠佢地自己"},{"pid":"8ddde0e19ac432bb7e2bdca7087dcd8e53c28973","tid":1743222,"uid":58958,"like":3,"disli